text: <!channel> We landed and all went well in New York! Since we've been up since before midnight PST we aren't going to make into the office, however. I'd love to do a quick check-in! How's everyone doing?
<@U02688JHZ>:  welcome back! so glad all went well. the cms is moving along. working on the backgrounds section, successfully uploading images, getting the slideshow put together.

Great. One of the things that we will need to provide to them soon will be some ideas/rough estimates for adding animations to the constellation images. That's not for next week's delivery, but to be implemented post-dogfood.

But yes, based on the conversations we already had on it, I don't expect changes, so that's fine but not necessarily high priority. Adam is out of the office this afternoon but I'll make sure we get written approval and any tweaks on Monday
